WEBVTT

00:02.204 --> 00:03.469
That boy'd make
a great boxer.

00:03.472 --> 00:04.771
No way you gonna
learn that boy

00:04.773 --> 00:06.039
in the ways of such
a savage sport.

00:06.041 --> 00:08.308
I hope you're
holding up.

00:08.310 --> 00:10.510
As well
as I can be.

00:10.512 --> 00:11.744
Good day.

00:12.518 --> 00:14.125
Look at
Mrs. Haverford.

00:14.126 --> 00:16.617
Corky seems... Smitten
with her, too.

00:16.742 --> 00:18.081
That would be
a very bad move.

00:18.206 --> 00:19.819
I don't really know
how to play the game.

